    public abstract class Bug
extends javafx.scene.shape.Circle
implements bugWorld.MovingObjects
    Version:
    1.0 Abstract class used to create bugs, which are actually extensions of the Circle class in Javafx and implements the MovingObjects interface
    Author:
    watsondyla

      • checkCollision

        public static boolean checkCollision(javafx.scene.shape.Shape s,
                                     javafx.scene.shape.Shape z)
        Collision detector.

        Creates a new shape which is the sum of the intersecting part of two shapes. If the new shapes width is 0, it means there's no intersection and therefore no collision.

        Parameters:
        s - Current bug
        z - Other shape in question
        Returns:
        boolean: colliding or not colliding
